RuntimeException              <|-- UnrecoverableException
IllegalArgumentException      <|-- InvalidArgumentException
UnsupportedOperationException <|-- NotSupportedOperationException

OpenMarkovRuntimeException  <|-- NonProjectablePotentialException
OpenMarkovRuntimeException  <|-- NotEvaluableNetworkException
OpenMarkovRuntimeException  <|-- InvalidNetworkTypeException
OpenMarkovRuntimeException  <|-- UnexpectedInferenceException
